text: I always love coming here. The staff are very accomodating & friendly. Even if they are about to close the shop, they will let you ahop & wait for you. They also have a wide variety of stuff from.different countries. I was amazed to find Filipino Bagoong, Suka, Toyo & various snacks.
super nice staff who are always friendly and if you're a regular theyll recognise you and talk to you a bit occasionally
Price are higher at this place
